<p><img src="/media/13078407/orient-express-collage-002.jpg" alt="" /></p>
<p>If you're travelling to any of our resorts in Italy's Lake Garda, you can travel out from London on the Venice Simplon Orient-Express and return by air from Verona. Alternatively, you can do the journey in reverse, travelling out by air and then returning home on the train.</p>
<br />
<div style="float: center;">
